@startuml

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title FTP: conexiune de control vs conexiune de date

actor Client
node "FTP Server" as S

Client -> S : TCP 21 (control)\nUSER/PASS, PWD, LIST, RETR/STOR
note right of S
Conexiune lunga
comenzi + raspunsuri
end note

Client -> S : TCP (data)\nLIST / RETR / STOR
note right of S
Conexiune separata
doar transfer efectiv
end note

@enduml